RAHU-MAN

Rahu-Men are Indian demigod-like beings of immense supernatural physical
power.  On Rifts Earth they exist as towering warriors with attributes that
put most OCC-eligible races to shame.  They tend toward intense personal
honor codes and are often found serving as protectors or champions.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 5-20   ME: 7-22   MA: 6-26   PS: 11-36 (Supernatural)
  PP: 7-22   PE: 8-28   PB: 5-20   Spd: 8-28

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 4d6 x10 (approx 40-240)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance (high values)
  - Enhanced vision: see further than most humanoids
  - Enhanced smell: detect threats by scent
  - Very high MA: naturally commanding presence

PENALTIES:
  - D-Bee classification by Coalition
  - Large size; cannot use standard human equipment

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

